data.text: THE PRINCIPAL CONTENTS OF ALDERLEY HOUSE to be sold at the Stansted Mountfitchet Auction Rooms Tuesday 23 July 2019 at 10am ORDER OF SALE Lots 1 - 9 Entrance Hall Lots 10 - 38 Drawing Room Lots 39 - 59 Dining Room Lots 60 - 126 Library Lots 127 - 147 Sitting Room Lots 148 - 166 Study Lots 167 - 179 Kitchens Lots 180 - 210 Estate Office, Boot Room and Entrance to the Gardens Lots 211 - 220 Staircase Lots 221 - 235 Bedroom One Lots 236 - 246 Bedroom Two Lots 247 - 261 Bedroom Three Lots 262 - 272 Bedroom Four Lots 273 - 337 Remaining Bedrooms Lots 338 - 361 Playroom, Bedroom Sitting Area and Remaining Contents The residual contents will be sold in the Homes and Interiors Sale on 20 August VIEWING TIMES Saturday 20 July 10am - 1pm Sunday 21 July 10am - 1pm Monday 22 July 9am - 5pm Tuesday 23 July From 9am ONLINE BIDDING Bid live at www.sworder.co.uk (3% surcharge) FURTHER INFORMATION Telephone: 01279 817778 Email: auctions@sworder.co.uk
